{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "5c682dc6-2995-4111-a4a1-b6928ff8b56a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c682dc6-2995-4111-a4a1-b6928ff8b56a@1.pkg/1772597479083/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597480105", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c682dc6-2995-4111-a4a1-b6928ff8b56a@1.pkg/1772597479083/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597480105"}, "identifier": "5c682dc6-2995-4111-a4a1-b6928ff8b56a", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对 &ldquo;回望成长&rdquo; 中奋斗精神与人生信念的认识和把握。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：王丹虽身有残疾，但凭借坚定信念和不懈奋斗实现成长目标，体现了成长过程中信念与奋斗的重要性，符合 &ldquo;在回望成长中懂得奋斗对实现人生价值的意义&rdquo; 这一知识点，故 B 正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：&ldquo;只要&hellip;&hellip; 就能&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo; 表述绝对，奋斗是克服困难的重要因素，但并非唯一，故 A 错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：王丹在自身努力的同时还帮助同学，说明成长中应兼顾个人与他人，该选项说法错误，故 C 错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：&ldquo;只能依靠个人努力&rdquo; 忽略了社会、他人的支持作用，说法片面，故 D 错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&ldquo;新时代好少年&rdquo; 王丹腿部残疾，却以 &ldquo;靠奋斗走出大山&rdquo; 为信念，初中三年坚持提前到校早读，帮同学辅导功课，最终考入重点高中，还带动班级形成 &ldquo;互助奋进&rdquo; 学风。这启示我们（&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）“新时代好少年” 王丹腿部残疾，却以 “靠奋斗走出大山” 为信念，初中三年坚持提前到校早读，帮同学辅导功课，最终考入重点高中，还带动班级形成 “互助奋进” 学风。这启示我们（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c682dc6-2995-4111-a4a1-b6928ff8b56a@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984729220", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">只要努力奋斗，就能克服一切困难</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">成长路上需坚定信念，用奋斗书写青春</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">关注自身发展即可，不必关心他人</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">残疾学生的成长只能依靠个人努力</span></p></div>"